# ─── Lokal (development) ───
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=3306
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=
DB_NAME=poltekimipas
# Prisma & migrasi memakai satu URL:
DATABASE_URL="mysql://root:@127.0.0.1:3306/poltekimipas"

# ─── Vercel (Production) + Railway MySQL ───
# 1) Buat database MySQL di Railway; di tab Variables salin nilai host, port, user, password, database.
# 2) Di Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables → Environment: Production
#    isi DB_HOST, DB_PORT, DB_USER, DB_PASSWORD, DB_NAME agar SAMA dengan Railway.
# 3) DATABASE_URL untuk Prisma (format mysql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE)
#    contoh: mysql://root:PASSWORD@containers-us-west-xxx.railway.app:3306/railway
# 4) Deploy: Vercel otomatis memakai variabel Production; lokal tetap memakai file .env (jangan di-commit).
# 5) Setelah deploy: jalankan migrasi dari mesin lokal dengan DATABASE_URL Railway, atau pakai
#    "prisma migrate deploy" di Vercel Build Command jika Anda sertakan URL hanya di Vercel.
